      "content": "While the sensation of taste or feeling like you drank it is certainly vivid, it is more likely an intense form of dream-memory recall rather than external projection. Dreams are highly sophisticated internal narratives, and the intensity you feel suggests a powerful emotional connection to the imagery, possibly linked to underlying stress or subconscious triggers. If these episodes become distressing or significantly disrupt your sleep, speaking with a sleep specialist or therapist would be the best step.",
      "source": "target",
